  # Nerd Font Symbols Preset [​](https://starship.rs/presets/nerd-font\#nerd-font-symbols-preset)
  
  This preset changes the symbols for each module to use Nerd Font symbols.
  
  ![Screenshot of Nerd Font Symbols preset](https://starship.rs/presets/img/nerd-font-symbols.png)
  
  ### Prerequisites [​](https://starship.rs/presets/nerd-font\#prerequisites)
  
  - A [Nerd Font](https://www.nerdfonts.com/) installed and enabled in your terminal (the example uses Fira Code Nerd Font)
  
  ### Configuration [​](https://starship.rs/presets/nerd-font\#configuration)
  
  sh
  
  ```
  starship preset nerd-font-symbols -o ~/.config/starship.toml
  ```
  
  [Click to download TOML](https://starship.rs/presets/toml/nerd-font-symbols.toml)
  
